			<CASNumber>10028-22-5</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Ferric sulfate is produced by adding sulfuric acid and an oxidizing agent to a hot solution of ferrous sulfate. It is used to make iron alums and other ferric compounds; as a coagulant in water. Ferrous sulfate is a type of iron that becomes a part of your hemoglobin and myoglobin in your body. It is an essential body mineral.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">硫酸铁是在硫酸亚铁的热溶液中加入硫酸和氧化剂而生成的。它可用于制造铁明矾和其他铁化合物，也可用作水的凝结剂。硫酸亚铁是一种铁，在人体内会成为血红蛋白和肌红蛋白的一部分。它是人体必需的矿物质。</common:generalComment>
